                    <span class="text-sm line-through opacity-50">$900.000 CLP</span>
                    <span class="text-base font-bold text-gray-900">$450.000 CLP</span>
                    <span class="bg-yellow-400 text-white text-sm px-2 py-1 rounded-md w-max">50.0%! Descuento!</span>
                </div>
                <div class="p-4 pt-0">
                <a href="./blog/bajo-cort-a5p.html#amplificador_cort_a5p" class="bg-red-400 hover:bg-red-500 text-white text-sm font-semibold px-4 py-2 rounded-lg shadow transition-colors duration-300 w-full block text-center">Ver detalles</a>
